OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782262075
OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FEngland fans were left frustrated at a
OL,7,Fgoalless draw as Thomas Tuchel's team
OL,8,Fstruggled to break through Ghana's
OL,9,Fdefence amid more hydration break
OL,10,Fcontroversy.
OL,12,FEngland fans flocked to watch parties
OL,13,Fin Wembley, Manchester, Nottingham and
OL,14,FNewcastle ahead of the match at the
OL,15,FGillette Stadium in Boston on Tuesday
OL,16,Fevening.
OL,18,FThe heat didn't keep fans away after
OL,19,Ftemperatures reached 34.6C in the UK
OL,20,Fearlier in the day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
