CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782262075
OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FMany donned England shirts and some
OL,7,Fwere seen with handheld fans, while
OL,8,Fothers wore hats to stay cool.
OL,10,FFormer Arsenal midfielder Thomas
OL,11,FPartey was heavily booed by England
OL,12,Ffans and Djed Spence appeared to snub
OL,13,Fa handshake with the Ghana
OL,14,Finternational ahead of the clash in
OL,15,FBoston.
OL,17,FVideos on social media looked to show
OL,18,Fthe Tottenham defender refusing to put
OL,19,Fhis hand out to the 33-year-old after
OL,20,Fthe national anthems were sung.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
