OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782262075
OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FPartey returned to the Black Stars'
OL,7,Fstarting XI after missing last
OL,8,FWednesday's game with Panama in
OL,9,FToronto. He was denied entry to
OL,10,FCanada, having been charged with seven
OL,11,Fcounts of rape and one count of sexual
OL,12,Fassault in London between 2020 and
OL,13,F2022.
OL,15,FPartey told officials in the host
OL,16,Fcountry that he had never been
OL,17,Farrested or charged with a crime. He
OL,18,Fdenies all charges and is set to stand
OL,19,Ftrial next summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
