OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FThe first half saw stoppage time for
OL,7,Fan injury and instead of that being
OL,8,Fused for the hydration break, it was
OL,9,Fheld in the 26th minute in line with
OL,10,Fother games.
OL,12,FEngland supporters were very vocal and
OL,13,Floudly booing the mid-half drinks
OL,14,Fbreaks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
