OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782262075
OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FFifa told the Press Association that
OL,7,Fhydration breaks are implemented
OL,8,F"involving all teams in every match,
OL,9,Fso matches are played under the same
OL,10,Fconditions", adding: "We want to
OL,11,Fensure equal conditions for everyone,
OL,12,Fand that's why these breaks are
OL,13,Fimplemented in every match."
OL,15,FEngland failed to break down Ghana's
OL,16,Fdefence despite some late chances and
OL,17,Fended with a 0-0 draw.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@KO]rD@VOUuD@\O]
