OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FIt comes after England began their
OL,7,Fquest for global glory in memorable
OL,8,Ffashion by beating Croatia, then
OL,9,Franked 11th in the world, 4-2 in a
OL,10,FDallas thriller last Wednesday.
OL,12,FEngland fans with red and white
OL,13,Fclothing, face paint and hair dye
OL,14,Fbraved the rain in Boston ahead of the
OL,15,Fgame.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
