OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FA father and his two children, who
OL,7,Fwere dressed as three lions, have
OL,8,Falready spent #30,000 on their World
OL,9,FCup tournament journey and said they
OL,10,Ffelt like "something special" was
OL,11,Fhappening with the current team.
OL,13,FGlenn Hawkins, 61, from Cholsey in
OL,14,FOxfordshire, was with his son, Howard,
OL,15,F31, and 28-year-old daughter Eve.
OL,26,@rD@KOUrD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
