OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782262075
OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FAsked before the match if it was the
OL,7,Fmost optimistic he felt during a major
OL,8,Ftournament, Glenn Hawkins said: "I
OL,9,Fwould say so, yeah. They're under a
OL,10,Fgood manager ` good players, good
OL,11,Fsystem, good manager."
OL,13,FHoward added: "The first game really
OL,14,Fgot it going ` it went back home, big.
OL,15,FThere's something special happening
OL,16,Ffor sure."
OL,26,@pD@aOUsD@VO]uD@OOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
