OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782262075
OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FThe family, who have been to every
OL,7,Fmajor tournament with England since
OL,8,Fthe World Cup in Brazil in 2014, have
OL,9,Falready spent #30,000 on their latest
OL,10,Ftournament journey.
OL,12,FMr Hawkins said: "We started off in
OL,13,FMexico City for the opening match,
OL,14,Fthen we went to Monterrey for Tunisia
OL,15,Fagainst Sweden, then to Dallas for the
OL,16,FEngland game, then to Philadelphia for
OL,17,FHaiti against Brazil, then we've come
OL,18,Fhere."
OL,20,FEve added: "And hopefully a lot more
OL,21,Fto go."
OL,26,@tD@ROUzD@FO]|D@LOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
