OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782262075
OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FHoward said: "We're following until
OL,7,Fthey go out, which is the final when
OL,8,Fthey win it."
OL,10,FAsked how much the tournament had cost
OL,11,Fso far, Mr Hawkins said: "Don't,
OL,12,Fbecause the wife's watching. I paid
OL,13,Ffor three, and I'm already #30,000
OL,14,Fdeep."
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Andy Chard, who is in his
OL,17,F60s and originally from Stevenage in
OL,18,FHertfordshire, had the St George's
OL,19,Fcross painted across his face,
OL,20,Falongside 39-year-old Tim Chard.
OL,26,@nD@NOUpD@MO]sD@ZOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
