OL,3,CFans frustrated as England fail to
OL,4,Cbreak though Ghana defence
OL,6,FThe pair said they paid 600 dollars
OL,7,F(#453) for tickets to the game at the
OL,8,FGillette Stadium.
OL,10,FAndy said: "We bought them on the Fifa
OL,11,Fsite, we didn't want to take a chance."
OL,13,FSpeaking on England's chances for the
OL,14,Ftournament, Andy said: "I think they
OL,15,Fhave a good team, I like the manager.
OL,17,F"I'm not so sure about the defence,
OL,18,Fthough. I think they're a bit dodgy
OL,19,Fevery now and then ` but we've got
OL,20,Fenough firepower to overcome that.
OL,26,@rD@LOUsD@gO]vD@XOUyD@AOU
